    "Title": "Verified Bounty: ~mission(TargetName) at ~mission(Location)",
    "DisplayTitle": "Verified Bounty: [TargetName] at [Location]",
    "Description": "--------------------------------------------------------\n----------------- BOUNTY CONTRACT -----------------\n--------------------------------------------------------\n\nBOUNTY HUNTERS GUILD\nPROCESSING & DISTRIBUTION\n\nThe Bounty Hunters Guild has authorized an official bounty.\n\nNAME: ~mission(TargetName) \nSYSTEM: Stanton\nRISK ASSESSMENT: Medium\nLAST KNOWN LOCATION:  ~mission(Location|Address)\nKNOWN AFFILIATIONS: <None>\nNOTES: We have tracked this bounty target to the <EM4>Research wing</EM4> of an abandoned Associated Science and Development facility. While shuttered, various scavengers and other unsavory types are known to frequent the area.\n\nThe facility itself might also pose a risk as the nature of the research being conducted there is unknown. Be on the lookout for potential environmental hazards while in pursuit of the target.\n\n\nBOUNTY HUNTERS GUILD\nIn Pursuit of Justice\n\nThe Bounty Hunters Guild is a security service sanctioned by the Mercenary Guild and authorized to operate in both the UEE and beyond in accordance with Xenotrade Authority Acts.",
    "DisplayDescription": "--------------------------------------------------------\n----------------- BOUNTY CONTRACT -----------------\n--------------------------------------------------------\n\nBOUNTY HUNTERS GUILD\nPROCESSING & DISTRIBUTION\n\nThe Bounty Hunters Guild has authorized an official bounty.\n\nNAME: [TargetName] \nSYSTEM: Stanton\nRISK ASSESSMENT: Medium\nLAST KNOWN LOCATION:  [Location|Address]\nKNOWN AFFILIATIONS: <None>\nNOTES: We have tracked this bounty target to the <EM4>Research wing</EM4> of an abandoned Associated Science and Development facility. While shuttered, various scavengers and other unsavory types are known to frequent the area.\n\nThe facility itself might also pose a risk as the nature of the research being conducted there is unknown. Be on the lookout for potential environmental hazards while in pursuit of the target.\n\n\nBOUNTY HUNTERS GUILD\nIn Pursuit of Justice\n\nThe Bounty Hunters Guild is a security service sanctioned by the Mercenary Guild and authorized to operate in both the UEE and beyond in accordance with Xenotrade Authority Acts.",
